  "body": "### 1. letter-spacing\r\nLetter spacing currently used by the component doesn't match with letter spacing for Figma [design](https://www.figma.com/file/v98g9ZiaSHYUdKWrbFg9eM/Mobile-Foundations?node-id=617%3A208).\r\nAnd looks like small changes in letter spacing are not affecting the text component.\r\nFormula used by Figma for letter spacing: [formula](https://rsms.me/inter/dynmetrics/) ([ref](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/13753#discussion_r941192544))\r\n`Heading-1/Regular`\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/17097240/184025017-e8e663ca-6032-49b1-8080-486a5dd2578d.png\" alt=\"Screenshot\" height=\"300\"/>\r\n\r\n\r\n### 2. Line Height:\r\nThe line height currently used by the component doesn't match with line height from the Figma design\r\n`Paragraph-2/Regular`\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/17097240/184026205-c64ef274-85a9-4e49-baf6-f6bb83a560b7.png\" alt=\"Screenshot\" height=\"300\"/>\r\n\r\n[Original image]\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/17097240/184026699-c641aabc-19d2-4129-8beb-292343f4141d.png\" alt=\"Screenshot\" height=\"200\"/>\r\n\r\n",
